- Add PyQtGraph example;
- Add info in README;
- Fix comparison between QT_API and PYQTGRAPH_QT_LIB;
- Set selected tab background color to light one;
- Add a blue bar on selected tab;
- Remove left space to fit tabs (mainly east and west).

Parallelly run Python 2 and 3 unit tests.
This will save around 45 minutes of build time in Jenkins.

